  "prompt": "I am going to organising an party, for that I need to clean my home on or before 31/12/2017. So suggest me cleaning service company in Perth?",
  "response": "Organizing a party and ensuring your home is clean and presentable is essential. Here are some reputable cleaning service companies in Perth that you might consider:\n\n1. **Jim\u2019s Cleaning**\n   - **Overview:** Part of the nationally recognized Jim\u2019s group, they offer a range of cleaning services including residential cleaning, end-of-lease cleaning, and carpet cleaning.\n   - **Website:** [Jim\u2019s Cleaning Perth](https://www.jimscleaning.com.au/)\n\n2. **Absolute Domestics**\n   - **Overview:** Provides professional home cleaning services with customizable plans to fit your needs. They focus on reliability and customer satisfaction.\n   - **Website:** [Absolute Domestics](https://absolute-domestics.com.au/)\n\n3. **Fantastic Clean**\n   - **Overview:** Offers a variety of cleaning services including regular housekeeping, deep cleaning, and event-specific cleaning.\n   - **Website:** [Fantastic Clean](https://fantasticclean.com.au/)\n\n4. **Bee Clean**\n   - **Overview:** Specializes in eco-friendly cleaning solutions for homes and businesses, ensuring a safe environment for you and your family.\n   - **Website:** [Bee Clean Perth](https://bee-clean.com.au/)\n\n5. **Simply Clean**\n   - **Overview:** Provides comprehensive cleaning services with flexible scheduling options to accommodate your party preparations.\n   - **Website:** [Simply Clean Perth](https://simplycleanperth.com.au/)\n\n6. **Molly Maid**\n   - **Overview:** An internationally recognized cleaning service that offers tailored cleaning plans to meet your specific requirements.\n   - **Website:** [Molly Maid Perth](https://www.mollymaid.com.au/locations/perth.aspx)\n\n7. **Urban Helpers**\n   - **Overview:** Offers a wide range of domestic cleaning services, including pre-event cleaning to ensure your home is party-ready.\n   - **Website:** [Urban Helpers](https://urbanhelpers.com.au/)\n\n**Tips for Choosing the Right Cleaning Service:**\n\n- **Check Reviews:** Look for customer testimonials and reviews on platforms like Google, Yelp, or Facebook to gauge the quality of service.\n- **Compare Quotes:** Request quotes from multiple companies to compare pricing and services offered.\n- **Verify Credentials:** Ensure the company is licensed, insured, and employs trained professionals.\n- **Specify Your Needs:** Clearly communicate your cleaning requirements and the timeline, especially since you have a specific date in mind.\n- **Ask About Eco-Friendly Options:** If sustainability is important to you, inquire if they use environmentally friendly cleaning products.\n\n**Contacting the Service:**\nIt's advisable to contact the cleaning companies as soon as possible to confirm their availability for your desired date (on or before December 31, 2023). Booking in advance ensures you secure a spot, especially during busy seasons.\n\nI hope this helps you find the perfect cleaning service for your party preparations! If you need further assistance, feel free to ask.",
